<h1><b>Volunteer in an organization that is in line with your interests. </b><b>You're more likely to identify your next steps or "calling" sooner by doing something (even when not getting paid) rather than sitting at home doing nothing.</b></h1>
<div style={{width: "50%",float: "right"}}>
<StaticImage
  src="../../../images/volunteer.jpg"
/>
</div>
<ul>
<li><h2><b>Gives you an opportunity to learn more about your field of interest, build practical skills and cultivate opportunities.</b></h2></li>
<li><h2><b>Helps you gain more work experience.</b></h2></li>
<li><h2><b>Broadens your network of connections.</b></h2></li>
<li><h2><b>The supervisor or other colleagues can provide you with a job reference.</b></h2></li>
</ul>
